results.name: Number of partitions of n^2 into squares greater than 1.
link: Alois P. Heinz, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..500
mathematica: b[n_, i_] := b[n, i] = If[n == 0, 1, If[i<2, 0, b[n, i-1] + If[i^2>n, 0, b[n-i^2, i]]]]; a[n_] := b[n^2, n]; Table[a[n], {n, 0, 50}] (* _Jean-François Alcover_, Nov 11 2015, after _Alois P. Heinz_ *)
results.author: _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Mar 19 2004
ext: Corrected a(0) and more terms from _Alois P. Heinz_, Apr 15 2013
